original: Let's get didgetal! Try out our new electric didgeridoo.  Annoy the neighbors and get microdermabrasion at the same time!
translated: 来点数码迪吉吧！试一试我们的新款电子迪吉里杜管。一边骚扰邻居，一边体验微晶磨皮吧！

original: Didgeridoo Carrying Cases: protect your instrument and look like you're carrying a huge hunting rifle! A great way to scare people in airports.
translated: 迪吉里杜管收纳盒：保护你的乐器，让你看起来像是背着把巨大的猎枪！很适合用来在机场吓人。

original: Didgeridoo Lessons! Pay to learn how to play one note over and over again. Kids, your parents will love it!
translated: 迪吉里杜课程！付费学习如何反复吹奏同一个音。孩子们，你的父母会喜欢的！
